\u8a9e \u5b8c\u6210\u7248 \u6a2a\u3011\u30e1\u30a4\u30f3\u30d2\u3099\u30b7\u3099\u30e5\u30a2\u30eb.png", "id": "762478728591491", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982441_762478731924824_3731905345530924161_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jm5KLUdmj9MQ7kNvgECAF41&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDbwVU0PqDkiQuX6tB9cPnaLhuv__R9hOWA03yxj6_rww&oe=66D06079"}, "display_name": "Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable", "keywords": ["AttackonTitan", "AoT", "Shingeki", "Action", "Hunting"], "long_description": "Fight for your life against man-eating Titans in Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable. In a thrilling mix of hunting and action, join the Scout Regiment and put on your Omni Directional Mobility Gear to defend and protect humanity against the Titans. \n\nFeatures:\n\nExhilarating Flight Experience: Get ready for a unique adventure with UNIVRS\u2019 anti-motion sickness technology that will help bring the thrilling cross-range combat against killer Titans to life.\n\nMultiplayer: Team up with another member of the Scout Regiment in two-player co-op or go solo in the fight for humanity. \n\nDevise a strategy: There will be a number of enemies out to get you. With a wider range of weapons at your disposal, devise and execute the best plan to cut down the Titan population in the city.\n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd.   \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.", "short_description": "Fight for your life against man-eating Titans in Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable. In a thrilling mix of hunting and action, join the Scout Regiment and put on your Omni Directional Mobility Gear to defend and protect humanity against the Titans. \n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd.   \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc."}]}, "developer_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://univrs.jp/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "UNIVRS, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://aotvrub.com/", "category": "GAMES", "co